%^BOLD%^-=%^GREEN%^Renewal Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

The renewal domain deals with returning things to the state they once held.  The domain culminates in the ability to cast healing spells that are otherwise unavailable to divine casters.

Clerics with the Renewal Domain gain the following benefits:
- A +2 bonus to caster level when casting healing school spells.

The renewal domain contains the following spells:

Rejuvenation, Breath of Life, Greater Heal, Regenerate, Greater Mass Heal

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Jarmila, Nimnavanon

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
